One Chat Intro: OneChat is a GPT client that supports mobile phones, and tablets. It's easy to use with simple configuration for OpenAI's API. Supported models include OpenAI models (such as gpt-3.5-turbo, gpt-3.5-turbo-16k, gpt-4, gpt-4-32k). Welcome to use!
buytips: OneChat is a client that supports the currently popular large language models. It currently supports the OpenAI official API and the OpenAI models deployed on Azure. Users can choose to configure their own API access points or use OneChat's default services. OneChat aims to make it easy for everyone to use, and the model usage pricing is consistent with the official pricing.
Model name deployed on Azure: Deployment name and URL for the model deployed on Azure correspond to the EndPoint of the Azure resource.
model intro: OneChat only support GPT3.5, GPT4 models. Google Bard and Gemini models will be supported in the future.
